abstract: >-
  A single repository integrating 6 independent AI rule systems (coding,
  conversation, novel, interactive-novel, paper, agent-builder) with a shared
  core layer, 14 composable capability packs (incl. DAR domain authority
  registry), and multi-tool sync to 13 platforms (Claude Code, Gemini, Cursor,
  GitHub Copilot, Trae, Windsurf, Cline, Continue, Amazon Q, Qodo, Tongyi
  Lingma, Comate, plus cross-tool AGENTS.md standard). Incorporates
  research-backed prompt engineering and safety guardrails.
keywords:
